1
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:20,640
Xuezhi!

2
00:00:21,960 --> 00:00:22,519
Xuezhi!

3
00:00:23,199 --> 00:00:24,160
Xuezhi, wake up!

4
00:00:24,679 --> 00:00:25,239
Xuezhi!

5
00:00:26,320 --> 00:00:26,879
Xinyue!

6
00:00:27,280 --> 00:00:28,000
Sister Su!

7
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:30,239
Slow down.

8
00:00:36,640 --> 00:00:37,039
Xue...

9
00:00:37,280 --> 00:00:38,399
Xuezhi!

10
00:00:41,119 --> 00:00:41,880
Yan Ge!

11
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,039
Get the medical tools!

12
00:00:44,399 --> 00:00:44,960
Sister Su.

13
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:45,880
Hot water.

14
00:01:18,560 --> 00:01:19,560
Whether she can wake up

15
00:01:21,680 --> 00:01:22,599
depends on tonight.

16
00:01:25,599 --> 00:01:27,879
What if she refuses to take the medicine?

17
00:01:28,640 --> 00:01:30,519
What if she refuses to take the medicine?

18
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:33,239
I don't want...

19
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:37,400
I don't want you to leave me, Xuezhi.

20
00:01:43,319 --> 00:01:44,359
Xuezhi.

21
00:01:45,000 --> 00:01:46,200
Xuezhi, you're awake.

22
00:01:46,640 --> 00:01:48,959
You're finally awake.

23
00:01:49,719 --> 00:01:50,480
I...

24
00:01:51,879 --> 00:01:54,599
I dreamt that Mr. Cui came to pick me up.

25
00:01:55,159 --> 00:01:56,879
He brought the betrothal gifts

26
00:01:57,519 --> 00:01:58,760
and a grand wedding procession.

27
00:01:59,719 --> 00:02:02,159
He took me through the front door.

28
00:02:02,840 --> 00:02:03,359
Yan...

29
00:02:03,959 --> 00:02:04,959
Yan Ge,

30
00:02:05,719 --> 00:02:08,240
I'm afraid I won't be able to wait for him.

31
00:02:09,599 --> 00:02:10,960
Could you help me

32
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:14,319
take my dowry to him?

33
00:02:15,439 --> 00:02:16,400
Tell him

34
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:18,000
on my behalf,

35
00:02:18,879 --> 00:02:20,120
thank him.

36
00:02:21,080 --> 00:02:22,879
If there's a next life,

37
00:02:23,599 --> 00:02:25,560
I'd still marry him.

38
00:02:32,919 --> 00:02:33,439
Xuezhi!

39
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:36,639
Xuezhi!

40
00:02:41,039 --> 00:02:41,639
Xuezhi!

41
00:02:45,240 --> 00:02:46,960
Xuezhi!

42
00:03:10,280 --> 00:03:11,000
Xuezhi!

43
00:03:11,000 --> 00:03:12,759
Don't leave me!

44
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:14,680
Xuezhi.

45
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,080
Xuezhi.

46
00:03:25,919 --> 00:03:28,479
You always said I stole your thunder,

47
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:31,280
but whenever I was punished...

48
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:33,840
Eat up.

49
00:03:34,280 --> 00:03:35,080
If you starve,

50
00:03:35,199 --> 00:03:36,360
who will save my face?

51
00:03:36,879 --> 00:03:38,560
You sneakily gave me tasty treats.

52
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,800
Do you remember

53
00:03:54,199 --> 00:03:57,159
when you took me out for fun?

54
00:03:59,879 --> 00:04:02,199
[You always bought me]

55
00:04:02,879 --> 00:04:04,400
[what you liked.]

56
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:08,159
[You always faced me with such innocence]

57
00:04:09,000 --> 00:04:10,120
[and gave me hope]

58
00:04:10,719 --> 00:04:11,520
[and strength.]

59
00:04:31,800 --> 00:04:32,600
You're so annoying.

60
00:04:32,600 --> 00:04:34,480
It's really worth spending money on you.

61
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,480
I'll come back early to see you.

62
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,600
What surprise

63
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,759
do you have for me today?

64
00:04:41,279 --> 00:04:41,879
Stop it.

65
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,199
Go.

66
00:04:52,079 --> 00:04:53,079
What's wrong with you?

67
00:04:53,199 --> 00:04:54,040
Who are you?

68
00:04:54,040 --> 00:04:55,879
You have a wife,

69
00:04:55,879 --> 00:04:58,040
yet you still dare to deceive women at Ming Yue Pavilion

70
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,120
to keep their chastity for you.

71
00:04:59,560 --> 00:04:59,839
Shh.

72
00:04:59,839 --> 00:05:00,759
Keep your voice down.

73
00:05:00,759 --> 00:05:02,600
Do you know she was pregnant with your child

74
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:04,360
and was killed?

75
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,759
She was just a courtesan.

76
00:05:09,920 --> 00:05:11,759
Who knows whose child it was?

77
00:05:12,199 --> 00:05:14,279
We were just playing around.

78
00:05:14,839 --> 00:05:16,040
Who do you think you are,

79
00:05:16,319 --> 00:05:17,879
coming to break up my family?

80
00:05:18,319 --> 00:05:20,120
You have the nerve to do it but not to admit it?

81
00:05:21,319 --> 00:05:23,439
She was still thinking of you when she died,

82
00:05:24,480 --> 00:05:26,800
and left everything to you.

83
00:05:27,879 --> 00:05:29,000
She loved you so much

84
00:05:29,279 --> 00:05:30,720
that she even gave her life.

85
00:05:32,319 --> 00:05:34,519
and you don't even shed a tear!

86
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,639
What did she leave me?

87
00:05:36,959 --> 00:05:37,600
Is this it?

88
00:05:37,959 --> 00:05:39,000
This is Xuezhi's stuff!

89
00:05:39,000 --> 00:05:39,839
Don't even think about it!

90
00:05:39,839 --> 00:05:40,759
What did she leave you?

91
00:05:40,759 --> 00:05:41,240
Let go!

92
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:43,600
You want Xuezhi's stuff?

93
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:44,759
You're a liar!

94
00:05:45,160 --> 00:05:45,959
Tell me,

95
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:47,160
what else do you want?

96
00:05:47,439 --> 00:05:48,800
These are all Xuezhi's things.

97
00:05:48,879 --> 00:05:49,639
How dare you!

98
00:05:54,439 --> 00:05:55,240
What happened?

99
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,439
Go away.

100
00:06:10,920 --> 00:06:11,759
My lady.

101
00:06:12,920 --> 00:06:13,399
My lady.

102
00:06:14,040 --> 00:06:15,839
Don't listen to those bitches.

103
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:17,680
I'm truly into you.

104
00:06:21,279 --> 00:06:21,720
No.

105
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,040
Take care.

106
00:06:37,279 --> 00:06:38,360
This doesn't smell right.

107
00:06:39,040 --> 00:06:39,639
Wait a moment.

108
00:06:51,319 --> 00:06:52,000
Please wait a moment.

109
00:06:59,319 --> 00:06:59,879
What is this?

110
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,240
Peucedanum praeruptorum.

111
00:07:03,399 --> 00:07:04,000
And what is this?

112
00:07:04,759 --> 00:07:06,680
This is also Peucedanum praeruptorum.

113
00:07:15,160 --> 00:07:16,839
This is Isatis root fumigated with sulfur.

114
00:07:20,439 --> 00:07:23,279
Peucedanum praeruptorum is ten times more expensive than Isatis root.

115
00:07:24,279 --> 00:07:27,399
These herbs were delivered by Ren'an Hall.

116
00:07:28,319 --> 00:07:31,079
How could Mr. Xiao do such a thing?

117
00:07:32,879 --> 00:07:33,839
He must be unaware of this.

118
00:07:34,240 --> 00:07:35,319
He would never allow

119
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,639
substandard medicine for profit.

120
00:07:37,639 --> 00:07:38,560
Seal the medicine.

121
00:07:39,079 --> 00:07:39,920
I'll go to Ren'an Hall.

122
00:07:42,519 --> 00:07:43,639
People who took Guiyuan Pills

123
00:07:43,879 --> 00:07:45,120
are either vomiting sour water

124
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,639
or having difficulty breathing.

125
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:49,040
They are all my regular customers.

126
00:07:49,279 --> 00:07:50,920
When Xiao Lang was alive,

127
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,199
this never happened.

128
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:55,560
The Xiao Family, for profit,

129
00:07:56,040 --> 00:07:57,120
passed off inferior goods

130
00:07:57,399 --> 00:07:58,519
and endangered lives.

131
00:07:59,000 --> 00:08:00,439
If you don't give us an explanation today,

132
00:08:00,639 --> 00:08:02,519
we can't continue doing business.

133
00:08:03,160 --> 00:08:03,600
Everyone,

134
00:08:04,519 --> 00:08:06,839
I will investigate this thoroughly

135
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,040
and give you an explanation.

136
00:08:08,600 --> 00:08:11,360
All losses will be borne by the Ren'an Hall.

137
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,319
You've worked with us for years.

138
00:08:14,199 --> 00:08:15,360
Please bear with us.

139
00:08:18,079 --> 00:08:19,319
If you don't mind,

140
00:08:19,920 --> 00:08:21,879
let me check your pulse.

141
00:08:22,560 --> 00:08:23,680
I'll do my best to treat you.

142
00:08:23,680 --> 00:08:25,279
Why should we trust you?

143
00:08:25,959 --> 00:08:27,199
Are you trying to

144
00:08:27,519 --> 00:08:28,800
pin this on someone

145
00:08:29,160 --> 00:08:30,319
and kill us

146
00:08:30,639 --> 00:08:32,080
to cover it up?

147
00:08:32,279 --> 00:08:33,080
Am I right?

148
00:08:33,159 --> 00:08:34,360
If you don't trust me,

149
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,440
let me treat someone right here.

150
00:08:36,639 --> 00:08:37,399
If it doesn't work,

151
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:38,519
you can do whatever you want with me.

152
00:08:38,919 --> 00:08:40,039
Easy for you to say.

153
00:08:40,360 --> 00:08:42,159
Who would risk their lives

154
00:08:42,159 --> 00:08:43,440
with someone like you?

155
00:08:43,759 --> 00:08:44,559
Besides,

156
00:08:44,879 --> 00:08:45,679
since ancient times,

157
00:08:45,879 --> 00:08:47,879
women have never been allowed to practice medicine.

158
00:08:48,279 --> 00:08:50,039
Ren'an Hall must be closed!

159
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,000
Close it!

160
00:08:51,080 --> 00:08:51,879
Yes, close it!

161
00:08:52,159 --> 00:08:53,200
Close it!

162
00:08:53,559 --> 00:08:54,320
Where's the Guiyuan Elixir?

163
00:09:04,600 --> 00:09:05,240
Are you crazy?

164
00:09:09,600 --> 00:09:10,759
Now I'm just like everyone else,

165
00:09:11,399 --> 00:09:12,440
I've taken the Guiyuan Elixir.

166
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,360
Since you don't want to believe me,

167
00:09:14,480 --> 00:09:15,039
just watch

168
00:09:15,399 --> 00:09:16,559
if I get poisoned or not.

169
00:09:16,559 --> 00:09:17,120
She's crazy!

170
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:18,159
This woman is insane!

171
00:09:18,399 --> 00:09:19,399
I'll tell everyone

172
00:09:19,600 --> 00:09:20,679
that Ren'an Hall has hired a madman

173
00:09:21,039 --> 00:09:21,919
to kill us!

174
00:09:23,200 --> 00:09:23,759
Stop him!

175
00:09:27,919 --> 00:09:28,879
I'm sorry, everyone.

176
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:31,240
I mean no harm.

177
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,799
But if you leave,

178
00:09:34,159 --> 00:09:36,039
Ren'an Hall will be accused

179
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,519
of hiring killers.

180
00:09:37,960 --> 00:09:38,840
for hiring killers.

181
00:09:39,759 --> 00:09:41,480
Ren'an Hall may have made mistakes,

182
00:09:41,879 --> 00:09:42,799
but as a healer,

183
00:09:43,279 --> 00:09:44,840
I genuinely wish to help everyone.

184
00:09:46,240 --> 00:09:47,200
I swear on my life

185
00:09:47,279 --> 00:09:47,879
and the medicine.

186
00:09:48,360 --> 00:09:49,039
I only ask

187
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,080
for a chance

188
00:09:52,000 --> 00:09:52,639
to retrieve the recipe

189
00:09:55,399 --> 00:09:56,519
for Guiyuan Pills.

190
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:42,720
Go get the bowl.

191
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,639
Licorice, ginger, and mung bean soup.

192
00:10:53,519 --> 00:10:54,840
The original recipe is correct,

193
00:10:55,759 --> 00:10:56,679
but the dosage of aconite

194
00:10:57,720 --> 00:10:59,039
in the medicine

195
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,200
exceeded the original amount,

196
00:11:02,200 --> 00:11:03,320
causing toxicity.

197
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:22,759
Just double the dosage of these two,

198
00:11:23,200 --> 00:11:24,440
and add mung beans to clear the remaining toxins.

199
00:11:25,279 --> 00:11:26,240
Use the original recipe

200
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:28,000
to counter its excessiveness.

201
00:11:38,960 --> 00:11:39,600
Wait a moment.

202
00:11:39,919 --> 00:11:41,080
Drink the medicine before you leave.

203
00:11:58,120 --> 00:11:59,639
If it's just mung bean soup,

204
00:11:59,840 --> 00:12:00,480
I'll drink it.

205
00:12:00,679 --> 00:12:01,480
I'm willing too.

206
00:12:02,080 --> 00:12:02,879
I'm willing too.

207
00:12:02,879 --> 00:12:03,679
I'll drink it.

208
00:12:13,240 --> 00:12:14,000
Why are you in such a hurry to leave?

209
00:12:15,519 --> 00:12:16,360
Could it be that you're not sick?

210
00:12:17,960 --> 00:12:19,480
This person's pulse is slippery and floating,

211
00:12:20,840 --> 00:12:21,879
and their breathing is rapid.

212
00:12:22,320 --> 00:12:23,120
doesn't seem like an illness,

213
00:12:23,320 --> 00:12:24,039
but rather like guilt.

214
00:12:25,080 --> 00:12:25,960
I was just passing by,

215
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:26,960
and saw this injustice.

216
00:12:27,360 --> 00:12:28,200
Saw this injustice?

217
00:12:28,279 --> 00:12:28,720
Nong!

218
00:12:29,399 --> 00:12:29,840
Take him to the authorities!

219
00:12:30,679 --> 00:12:31,000
Move!

220
00:12:43,120 --> 00:12:43,559
My lord,

221
00:12:44,000 --> 00:12:45,200
the people from the pharmacy and warehouse

222
00:12:45,600 --> 00:12:46,360
the head of the warehouse

223
00:12:46,360 --> 00:12:47,639
hasn't shown up for three days.

224
00:12:51,120 --> 00:12:51,919
After you left,

225
00:12:52,360 --> 00:12:53,559
the business has fallen into chaos.

226
00:12:54,120 --> 00:12:55,320
I've been moving around

227
00:12:55,519 --> 00:12:56,639
different shops for months.

228
00:12:56,879 --> 00:12:57,519
Honestly,

229
00:12:57,840 --> 00:12:58,679
I'm overwhelmed.

230
00:12:59,080 --> 00:13:00,240
A few days ago, the head

231
00:13:00,559 --> 00:13:01,759
said his mother was gravely ill

232
00:13:01,879 --> 00:13:02,919
and needed to take a few days off.

233
00:13:03,519 --> 00:13:05,120
I didn't ask much.

234
00:13:06,480 --> 00:13:07,000
What are you pulling out?

235
00:13:08,320 --> 00:13:09,639
Aconite mixed with Astragalus.

236
00:13:10,679 --> 00:13:11,759
They're not hard to tell apart,

237
00:13:12,200 --> 00:13:13,200
but once ground into powder,

238
00:13:13,600 --> 00:13:15,279
even an experienced pharmacist

239
00:13:15,519 --> 00:13:16,240
would struggle to detect it.

240
00:13:17,279 --> 00:13:17,919
Moreover,

241
00:13:18,080 --> 00:13:19,879
the prescription already includes aconite,

242
00:13:20,399 --> 00:13:21,279
making it even harder to suspect.

243
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:26,919
It wasn't me!

244
00:13:29,159 --> 00:13:29,519
Speak up!

245
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:30,720
I'll tell you!

246
00:13:31,720 --> 00:13:32,879
Before A'Lang left,

247
00:13:33,320 --> 00:13:34,559
the head pharmacist came to me,

248
00:13:35,399 --> 00:13:35,799
saying

249
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,639
to take advantage of A'Lang's absence

250
00:13:38,159 --> 00:13:38,879
and make a profit.

251
00:13:39,279 --> 00:13:39,600
This...

252
00:13:39,799 --> 00:13:40,879
He also promised me

253
00:13:41,360 --> 00:13:42,399
that we wouldn't be found out.

254
00:13:43,279 --> 00:13:43,960
No one has noticed

255
00:13:43,960 --> 00:13:45,080
during this period of time.

256
00:13:46,399 --> 00:13:47,080
So the manager

257
00:13:47,320 --> 00:13:48,240
becomes more and more bold.

258
00:13:49,279 --> 00:13:49,919
Where is he?

259
00:13:50,879 --> 00:13:51,240
I...

260
00:13:51,879 --> 00:13:52,480
I don't know.

261
00:13:52,960 --> 00:13:54,000
I really don't know.

262
00:13:55,080 --> 00:13:55,519
Boss.

263
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:56,120
Boss.

264
00:13:56,120 --> 00:13:56,720
I'm sorry.

265
00:13:56,879 --> 00:13:58,120
I was forced by the steward.

266
00:13:58,360 --> 00:13:59,039
I'm sorry.

267
00:13:59,080 --> 00:13:59,840
I'm really sorry.

268
00:14:00,039 --> 00:14:00,960
I'll never do it again.

269
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:05,919
Kneel down.

270
00:14:07,159 --> 00:14:07,879
There won't be a next time.

271
00:14:08,759 --> 00:14:09,279
Take him away.

272
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:10,960
Get up.

273
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:12,159
Get up.

274
00:14:12,840 --> 00:14:13,120
Go.

275
00:14:14,000 --> 00:14:14,559
Shopkeeper,

276
00:14:15,519 --> 00:14:16,120
Recently,

277
00:14:16,639 --> 00:14:17,679
the herbs for the Women's Clinic

278
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:19,960
have been managed by the warehouse overseer.

279
00:14:20,639 --> 00:14:21,000
Yes.

280
00:14:21,519 --> 00:14:23,240
The overseer allocates them

281
00:14:23,600 --> 00:14:24,559
and the pharmacy boys deliver them.

282
00:14:25,320 --> 00:14:26,320
Is there a problem?

283
00:14:26,559 --> 00:14:27,080
Today,

284
00:14:27,679 --> 00:14:28,960
I found many sulfur-fumigated

285
00:14:29,240 --> 00:14:31,120
Isatis roots mixed in the herbs.

286
00:14:31,519 --> 00:14:32,519
Unless inspected carefully,

287
00:14:32,919 --> 00:14:34,000
they look very similar,

288
00:14:34,399 --> 00:14:35,320
and are hard to tell apart by eye.

289
00:14:35,720 --> 00:14:36,200
Sulfur is commonly used

290
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,000
to prevent pests in medicinal herbs.

291
00:14:38,399 --> 00:14:39,320
If the warehouse manager

292
00:14:39,320 --> 00:14:40,840
has been profiteering in this way for long,

293
00:14:41,320 --> 00:14:42,559
